com.avaje.ebean.config.dbplatform

Enum DbType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DbType>
      • com.avaje.ebean.config.dbplatform.DbType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<DbType>

    public enum DbType
extends Enum<DbType>
    The known DB types that are mapped.

    This includes extra types such as UUID, JSON, JSONB and HSTORE.
